                                        "title":  "Konjunktionen · Connecting Sentences",
                                        "text":  "Conjunctions connect clauses and sentences. German has two main types: coordinating (Hauptsatz + Hauptsatz) and subordinating (Hauptsatz + Nebensatz). The key difference is word order.",
